  "body": "[SaveState](https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/master/beacon-chain/db/state.go#L153) in DB package has a potential bug where we use the saving state's latest block header has key: https://github.com/prysmaticlabs/prysm/blob/master/beacon-chain/db/state.go#L178\r\n\r\nPer discussion with @prestonvanloon and @nisdas, we all agreed that the API should best off be `SaveState(state, blockRoot)` as the `blockRoot` refers to the what triggers the state. This API will also comply with the latest fork choice\r\n",
